reviewText:
If you are going to buy any one of these get this set, you will likely find something in there you didn't know you were missing. I saw about half of these before I got this collection and now that I've seen them all I really enjoyed the others.
There are a few issues in my opinion with the compression and mastering of them but not to many artifacts and the sound though average on most work ok if you are not using the default TV speakers. I have mine running though an amp and I am glad I did, you too might need the extra boost.
Fun little gems that are a bit under rated over all I think.
Great value for the price.  Campy 90's flicks, good picture and audio quality.
Ordered it for Wilder Napalm.  Cheaper to get this group of movies than just the single DVD.
Makes the wifey happy with the chick flicks. shipper did good

I bought this for Mating Habits of the Earthbound Human (love that movie!) and was really disappointed with the audio on this DVD. I had my TV turned up as high as it would go and the maximum volume on the DVD itself was slightly above a whisper. I had to go turn all the fans and other background noises off just to strain to here it. Never had any problem with any other DVDs or streaming videos. Whoever mastered the audio on this DVD was asleep at his desk. For shame.
